                            If you up-sell in the rightful manner, it can enhance the customers experience and therefor bring in more revenue for your business.
                            It’s highly beneficial as statistics show that the probability of selling to an existing customer is higher than selling to a new customer, as you have already build that relationship and trust with the existing customer.
                            <br /><br />
                           Once customers have completed there transaction, offer them related products that compliment their original purchase, or loyalty money off coupons.
</p>
